title: Florian Toplitsch
text:
Florian Toplitsch (born 7 September 1991) is an <a href="Austria">Austria</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for Völser SV.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Austrian%20Football%20First%20League">Austrian Football First League</a> debut for <a href="WSG%20Wattens">WSG Wattens</a> on 12 August 2016 in a game against <a href="SC%20Wiener%20Neustadt">SC Wiener Neustadt</a>.
In the summer of 2021, he joined Völser SV in the fourth-tier <a href="Tiroler%20Liga">Tiroler Liga</a>.
